    "description": {
      "es": "",
      "en": "Capture an exception for later rendering. The meaning of limit, lookup_lines and capture_locals are as for the StackSummary class. If compact is true, only data that is required by TracebackException’s format() method is saved in the class attributes. In particular, the __context__ field is calculated only if __cause__ is None and __suppress_context__ is false. Note that when locals are captured, they are also shown in the traceback. max_group_width and max_group_depth control the formatting ..."
